          "instructorActions": [
            "Greet student warmly: 'Good morning! Today we're covering short-field takeoff and maximum performance climb - essential for operations from airports with obstacles or limited runway length. This technique maximizes performance to clear obstacles with minimum ground roll and maximum climb angle.'",
