ight (reschedule for later when all factors are acceptable), Change aircraft (if maintenance issue resolved, use another aircraft), Change pilot (if pilot issue, have another pilot fly). Teaching point: If any PAVE factor is questionable, decision is NO-GO - don't rationalize concerns away, don't let external pressures affect decision. Have alternatives ready.'",
