ht bag) - won't interfere, accessible when needed. Emergency items: Known locations (fire extinguisher location checked, first aid kit location known, emergency checklist in knee board, ELT location known) - accessible in 10 seconds. Total time to access all items: 40 seconds (vs. 9 minutes disorganized). Teaching point: Organize cockpit before flight - consistent organization improves safety and efficiency. Time saved: 8 minutes 20 seconds per flight. Safety improved: No missed checklist items, no interference with controls, emergency items accessible. Efficiency improved: Tasks completed quickly, operations not delayed.'",
